%% Request-level state machine (4 states) for SandBox Booking Request records.

stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    [*] --> new_request: Form submission<br/>(External = 1)
    [*] --> new_request: Manual calendar event<br/>mirrored from Sandbox Calendar

    new_request --> confirmed: Staff approves<br/>→ Slack notify<br/>→ Gmail notify
    new_request --> hold: Staff needs more info
    new_request --> rejected: Staff rejects<br/>(reason optional)

    hold --> confirmed: Info received,<br/>staff approves
    hold --> rejected: Info received,<br/>staff rejects

    confirmed --> rejected: Cancellation<br/>(rare; runs cleanup)

    confirmed --> [*]: Google Calendar event<br/>created; slots marked;<br/>confirmation email sent
    rejected --> [*]: Rejection email sent;<br/>slots released

    note right of new_request
        Triggers on entry:
        - Slack message to DFZ channel
        - Gmail to staff list
    end note

    note right of confirmed
        Triggers on entry:
        - script 02 (booking range fill)
        - script 03 (setup/teardown/pending)
        - Google Calendar event creation
        - confirmation email
    end note

    note right of rejected
        Triggers on entry:
        - script 05 (rejection cleanup)
        - rejection email (with optional reason)
    end note
